Percy Kilbride https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Percy_Kilbride 0 Percy William Kilbride (July 16, 1888 – December 11, 1964) was an American character actor. He made a career of playing country hicks, most memorably as Pa Kettle in the Ma and Pa Kettle series of feature films.
